00:28:05,366 --> 00:28:06,726
The longer I hide it from you,

563
00:28:06,727 --> 00:28:08,096
the longer my happiness will last.

564
00:28:13,407 --> 00:28:15,016
Why did Lv Liang fall for you?

565
00:28:15,727 --> 00:28:17,417
What exactly does he like about you?

566
00:28:20,247 --> 00:28:21,217
Hongbin,

567
00:28:23,366 --> 00:28:25,616
I always wanted to ask you this.

568
00:28:26,647 --> 00:28:28,525
Am I, Jiang Jiaqiao,

569
00:28:28,526 --> 00:28:29,856
always

570
00:28:30,846 --> 00:28:32,977
a fool to you?

571
00:28:41,687 --> 00:28:42,536
It's fine.

572
00:28:42,566 --> 00:28:43,536
Forget it.

573
00:28:44,366 --> 00:28:45,457
Anyway,

574
00:28:46,407 --> 00:28:49,417
I feel elated
when I'm together with Lv Liang.

575
00:28:50,407 --> 00:28:52,137
I'm very happy.

576
00:28:53,846 --> 00:28:56,457
I've never been this happy
in my life before.

577
00:28:57,286 --> 00:28:58,177
Fine.

578
00:29:00,167 --> 00:29:01,776
I won't give you a single cent.

579
00:29:02,326 --> 00:29:04,045
I'll see if he'll still come back for you.

580
00:29:04,046 --> 00:29:05,096
Fine.

581
00:29:07,086 --> 00:29:09,737
You can freeze my bank cards again.

582
00:29:13,126 --> 00:29:14,296
Jiang Jiaqiao!

583
00:29:18,846 --> 00:29:19,726
If you dare to take one step

584
00:29:19,727 --> 00:29:20,856
out of the house,

585
00:29:22,046 --> 00:29:23,497
you better don't come back again!

586
00:29:29,766 --> 00:29:30,897
I'm serious.

587
00:29:37,647 --> 00:29:38,576
Hongbin,

588
00:29:40,007 --> 00:29:40,977
I'll be leaving now.

589
00:31:18,286 --> 00:31:19,816
(Deng Haiyang: The real estate agent
agreed to give you a refund.)

590
00:31:38,366 --> 00:31:39,296
Hello?

591
00:31:39,846 --> 00:31:40,897
Xiang Zhong?

592
00:31:41,407 --> 00:31:42,417
It's me.

593
00:31:42,967 --> 00:31:44,257
Where's Deng Haiyang?

594
00:31:46,687 --> 00:31:48,646
Haiyang was here just now.

595
00:31:48,647 --> 00:31:50,016
Xiang Zhong, don't worry.

596
00:31:50,526 --> 00:31:51,697
I'll look for him.

597
00:31:52,007 --> 00:31:53,006
I don't know

598
00:31:53,007 --> 00:31:54,257
what's wrong with him today.

599
00:31:54,326 --> 00:31:55,365
He didn't drink much,

600
00:31:55,366 --> 00:31:56,697
yet he had already
thrown up several times.

601
00:31:56,846 --> 00:31:57,897
Wait for a moment.

602
00:31:59,887 --> 00:32:00,737
Haiyang?

603
00:32:01,007 --> 00:32:02,177
Haiyang?

604
00:32:02,647 --> 00:32:03,525
Are you okay?

605
00:32:03,526 --> 00:32:04,616
Are you done?

606
00:32:04,887 --> 00:32:05,765
Can you guys

607
00:32:05,766 --> 00:32:07,616
stop drinking like this every day?

608
00:32:08,326 --> 00:32:09,217
Xiang Zhong,

609
00:32:09,967 --> 00:32:11,856
no one wants to do this, you know?

610
00:32:12,366 --> 00:32:13,697
We were finally able

611
00:32:14,286 --> 00:32:15,085
to ask

612
00:32:15,086 --> 00:32:17,177
the real estate manager out.

613
00:32:18,086 --> 00:32:20,336
And, he gave us
the refund for the rent.

614
00:32:21,007 --> 00:32:22,937
We have to thank him.

615
00:32:23,687 --> 00:32:24,246
Xiang Zhong,

616
00:32:24,247 --> 00:32:25,166
you can tell me first

617
00:32:25,167 --> 00:32:26,576
if you need anything.

618
00:32:27,046 --> 00:32:29,056
I still need to keep him company.

619
00:32:33,566 --> 00:32:34,536
It's nothing.

620
00:32:34,727 --> 00:32:36,296
Don't drink that much.

621
00:32:36,687 --> 00:32:37,616
Xiang Zhong,

622
00:32:37,887 --> 00:32:38,646
you don't need to worry

623
00:32:38,647 --> 00:32:40,536
when I'm here.

624
00:32:40,967 --> 00:32:42,697
I'll definitely
take good care of Haiyang.

625
00:32:43,247 --> 00:32:44,457
I'll drink as much

626
00:32:44,887 --> 00:32:46,376
as what Haiyang drinks.

627
00:32:47,566 --> 00:32:48,616
Haiyang,

628
00:32:49,447 --> 00:32:51,576
come out when you're done throwing up.

629
00:32:51,887 --> 00:32:53,457
Xiang Zhong, I'll hang up now.

630
00:33:10,566 --> 00:33:11,336
(Xiang Zhong: Thank you.)

631
00:33:21,687 --> 00:33:23,056
Mom.

632
00:33:23,487 --> 00:33:26,417
We'll be heading
to Grandma's house tomorrow.

633
00:33:26,447 --> 00:33:28,856
Will Dad come as well?

634
00:33:30,687 --> 00:33:32,257
You miss Dad, huh?

635
00:33:33,247 --> 00:33:34,897
Yeah.

636
00:33:36,407 --> 00:33:37,376
He will come.

637
00:33:37,447 --> 00:33:38,296
Go to sleep now.

638
00:33:39,046 --> 00:33:40,246
Good night, Mom.

639
00:33:40,247 --> 00:33:41,137
Good night.

640
00:34:15,007 --> 00:34:16,045
(You should return to Kunshan)

641
00:34:16,046 --> 00:34:17,577
(after your thesis defense tomorrow.)

642
00:34:17,887 --> 00:34:19,456
(Dad said we should
celebrate the occasion together.)

643
00:34:27,660 --> 00:34:29,990
(Gao Ping)

644
00:34:37,566 --> 00:34:38,856
(I wish you success.)

645
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:47,880
(Typing...)

646
00:34:57,560 --> 00:35:03,520
(Qian Feng)

647
00:35:25,007 --> 00:35:26,496
Qian Feng, what's wrong?

648
00:35:26,927 --> 00:35:27,816
Xiang Zhong,

649
00:35:28,086 --> 00:35:29,057
please come.

650
00:35:29,166 --> 00:35:30,816
Haiyang won't make it!

651
00:35:34,686 --> 00:35:35,816
What's wrong with him?

652
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:41,190
(Emergency Department)

653
00:35:45,847 --> 00:35:46,697
Qian Feng?

654
00:35:47,007 --> 00:35:47,856
Qian Feng!

655
00:35:48,287 --> 00:35:49,416
Qian Feng, wake up!

656
00:35:50,166 --> 00:35:50,926
Where's Deng Haiyang?

657
00:35:50,927 --> 00:35:51,936
What's going on?

658
00:35:53,166 --> 00:35:55,165
I think he's undergoing surgery
right now.

659
00:35:55,166 --> 00:35:55,846
I told you guys

660
00:35:55,847 --> 00:35:57,006
to not drink that much.

661
00:35:57,007 --> 00:35:57,725
Why must you guys drink

662
00:35:57,726 --> 00:35:58,605
so much?

663
00:35:58,606 --> 00:36:00,737
Xiang Zhong,
we didn't drink much this time.

664
00:36:00,967 --> 00:36:04,296
I think Haiyang
was in a bad mood lately.

665
00:36:04,327 --> 00:36:05,645
He threw up
after finishing his first glass.

666
00:36:05,646 --> 00:36:06,685
Why did you still let him drink, then?

667
00:36:06,686 --> 00:36:07,737
You should've kept an eye on him.

668
00:36:07,807 --> 00:36:08,605
The manager said bottoms up.

669
00:36:08,606 --> 00:36:10,137
We had to drink.

670
00:36:11,246 --> 00:36:12,217
Which of you is
Deng Haiyang's family member?

671
00:36:12,327 --> 00:36:13,045
Me.

672
00:36:13,046 --> 00:36:13,936
Come with me.

673
00:36:14,046 --> 00:36:15,376
Keep an eye on my bag.

674
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:20,160
(Critically Ill Notice)

675
00:36:24,007 --> 00:36:25,125
It's this serious?

676
00:36:25,126 --> 00:36:27,257
The patient had acute alcohol poisoning.

677
00:36:27,287 --> 00:36:29,326
We have already performed gastric lavage

678
00:36:29,327 --> 00:36:30,336
and administered some laxatives.

679
00:36:31,292 --> 00:36:32,121
However, the patient

680
00:36:32,122 --> 00:36:34,250
is still in a coma.

681
00:36:34,967 --> 00:36:37,486
His serum PH level

682
00:36:37,487 --> 00:36:38,697
is below 7.2.

683
00:36:38,726 --> 00:36:39,846
His blood pressure is unstable as well.

684
00:36:39,847 --> 00:36:40,806
The blood biochemistry indicators

685
00:36:40,807 --> 00:36:42,177
are still not quite normal.

686
00:36:43,086 --> 00:36:44,856
Look at the clauses below.

687
00:36:44,967 --> 00:36:45,966
If urgent intervention

688
00:36:45,967 --> 00:36:47,205
is needed,

689
00:36:47,206 --> 00:36:49,165
it'll involve intubating the patient

690
00:36:49,166 --> 00:36:50,537
or putting them on a ventilator.

691
00:36:50,566 --> 00:36:53,456
We need the signature of his family members
to proceed with the procedures.

692
00:36:54,887 --> 00:36:55,406
Doctor,

693
00:36:55,407 --> 00:36:57,217
please try your best to save him.

694
00:36:57,367 --> 00:36:58,456
I'm begging you here.

695
00:36:58,686 --> 00:36:59,446
Don't worry.

696
00:36:59,447 --> 00:37:00,896
We'll try our best.

697
00:37:01,046 --> 00:37:02,376
You should sign the paper first.

698
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,720
(Signature of Family: Xiang Zhong)

699
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:16,120
(Emergency Department)

700
00:37:21,086 --> 00:37:22,017
Xiang Zhong,

701
00:37:22,847 --> 00:37:24,976
should we call

702
00:37:25,166 --> 00:37:27,336
his mother and tell her about it?

703
00:37:32,807 --> 00:37:34,097
We should.

704
00:37:34,726 --> 00:37:35,896
You can call her.

705
00:37:35,967 --> 00:37:36,926
I assume she has blocked

706
00:37:36,927 --> 00:37:37,936
my contact number by now.

707
00:37:38,447 --> 00:37:40,177
Her phone is always off
during nighttime.

708
00:37:40,487 --> 00:37:41,537
Try and call her.

709
00:37:48,166 --> 00:37:48,926
Sorry.

710
00:37:48,927 --> 00:37:50,605
The number you have dialed
is unavailable.

711
00:37:50,606 --> 00:37:51,537
Xiang Zhong.

712
00:37:52,526 --> 00:37:53,936
Her phone is switched off.

713
00:37:55,927 --> 00:37:56,976
So,

714
00:37:57,847 --> 00:37:59,617
I suppose you're sober by now.

715
00:38:02,287 --> 00:38:03,886
Sorry for the trouble.

716
00:38:03,887 --> 00:38:05,257
Please look for his mother.

717
00:38:08,086 --> 00:38:09,017
This incident

718
00:38:09,206 --> 00:38:10,336
is quite serious.

719
00:38:11,407 --> 00:38:13,017
We can't make the call here.

720
00:38:13,246 --> 00:38:16,617
If anything does happen,

721
00:38:16,847 --> 00:38:20,245
we have to tell his mother

722
00:38:20,246 --> 00:38:21,326
to be mentally prepared.

723
00:38:21,327 --> 00:38:23,057
Xiang Zhong, it's fine.

724
00:38:23,166 --> 00:38:24,085
I'll go and find her.

725
00:38:24,086 --> 00:38:25,017
Don't worry.

726
00:38:26,206 --> 00:38:27,737
Take good care of yourself too.

727
00:38:28,407 --> 00:38:29,966
I'll hire a cab. Don't worry.

728
00:38:29,967 --> 00:38:30,657
See you.

729
00:38:31,086 --> 00:38:31,806
Safety first.

730
00:38:31,807 --> 00:38:33,137
Call me anytime if you need anything.

731
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,920
(Emergency Complex Building)

732
00:39:05,807 --> 00:39:06,896
Doctor, how is he?

733
00:39:07,086 --> 00:39:08,766
He has regained consciousness.

734
00:39:08,767 --> 00:39:09,565
His vital signs

735
00:39:09,566 --> 00:39:10,605
are stable now.

736
00:39:10,606 --> 00:39:11,376
This is great.

737
00:39:11,526 --> 00:39:12,326
We can transfer him

738
00:39:12,327 --> 00:39:13,137
to the Inpatient Department tomorrow.

739
00:39:13,447 --> 00:39:14,125
Thank you.

740
00:39:14,126 --> 00:39:15,006
- Thank you.
- Don't mention it.

741
00:39:15,007 --> 00:39:16,137
Let's handle the paperwork first.

742
00:39:44,566 --> 00:39:45,737
Hello, Xiang.

743
00:39:46,847 --> 00:39:48,936
Hello.

744
00:39:48,967 --> 00:39:49,846
Xiang.

745
00:39:49,847 --> 00:39:50,205
Hello.

746
00:39:50,206 --> 00:39:51,045
Xiang.

747
00:39:51,046 --> 00:39:51,976
Nice to meet you all.

748
00:39:53,206 --> 00:39:55,177
Xiang, come.

749
00:39:56,447 --> 00:39:57,296
Let's go and drink.

750
00:39:57,487 --> 00:39:58,376
I have no time.

751
00:39:58,807 --> 00:40:00,565
Today, Gao Ping

752
00:40:00,566 --> 00:40:02,296
will be graduating from his PhD study.

753
00:40:03,327 --> 00:40:05,856
That's an occasion worth celebrating.

754
00:40:05,967 --> 00:40:07,165
Which restaurant
do you guys plan to go to?

755
00:40:07,166 --> 00:40:08,416
Restaurant? We'll celebrate it at home.

756
00:40:08,487 --> 00:40:10,137
No restaurants out there
can compete with my cooking.

757
00:40:10,767 --> 00:40:11,577
Xiang,

758
00:40:11,686 --> 00:40:13,286
you can't afford

759
00:40:13,287 --> 00:40:14,697
to be stingy this time.

760
00:40:14,847 --> 00:40:16,006
You shouldn't try to save money.

761
00:40:16,007 --> 00:40:17,137
Go away.

762
00:40:17,447 --> 00:40:19,137
What do you mean by stingy?

763
00:40:19,206 --> 00:40:21,617
It only feels like a reunion
when we eat at home.

764
00:40:22,166 --> 00:40:23,846
A reunion, huh? Great.

765
00:40:23,847 --> 00:40:25,097
Alright.

766
00:40:25,126 --> 00:40:26,217
See you.

767
00:40:35,447 --> 00:40:36,296
Xiang Zhong?

768
00:40:36,887 --> 00:40:37,776
Xiang Zhong!

769
00:40:38,206 --> 00:40:39,217
Lower your volume.

770
00:40:42,166 --> 00:40:43,657
You came here so early in the morning.

771
00:40:43,847 --> 00:40:45,737
I'm still worried about Haiyang.

772
00:40:45,767 --> 00:40:47,045
- By the way,
- You...

773
00:40:47,046 --> 00:40:48,366
When I was on my way back yesterday,

774
00:40:48,367 --> 00:40:50,006
you called me and said
Haiyang was awake.

775
00:40:50,007 --> 00:40:51,617
I didn't look for his mother after that.

776
00:40:51,726 --> 00:40:52,766
I was worried that she might

777
00:40:52,767 --> 00:40:54,177
be worried after she found out.

778
00:40:54,767 --> 00:40:55,577
You have a point.

779
00:40:55,847 --> 00:40:56,966
Since you're here,

780
00:40:56,967 --> 00:40:58,366
you should deliver

781
00:40:58,367 --> 00:40:59,366
the rice soup
I bought at the breakfast shop

782
00:40:59,367 --> 00:41:00,125
to him.

783
00:41:00,126 --> 00:41:01,697
Doctor said he could
only take liquid food.

784
00:41:02,487 --> 00:41:03,336
Wait.

785
00:41:03,646 --> 00:41:04,645
You guys should remember this.

786
00:41:04,646 --> 00:41:05,685
Next time, no matter if
it's a drinking session

787
00:41:05,686 --> 00:41:07,685
or an important appointment,

788
00:41:07,686 --> 00:41:08,286
you guys

789
00:41:08,287 --> 00:41:09,565
mustn't drink that much again, okay?

790
00:41:09,566 --> 00:41:10,645
It'll kill you.

791
00:41:10,646 --> 00:41:11,416
Xiang Zhong.

792
00:41:11,807 --> 00:41:13,456
We didn't want to drink either.

793
00:41:13,606 --> 00:41:15,006
But we had no choice.

794
00:41:15,007 --> 00:41:16,097
We were asking them for a favor.

795
00:41:16,166 --> 00:41:17,006
If he wanted to drink,

796
00:41:17,007 --> 00:41:18,245
we had to drink with him.

797
00:41:18,246 --> 00:41:19,486
Besides, there was a huge issue

798
00:41:19,487 --> 00:41:21,137
with the house you rented.

799
00:41:21,206 --> 00:41:22,856
What issue?

800
00:41:23,686 --> 00:41:25,286
I'll deliver this to him first.

801
00:41:25,287 --> 00:41:26,376
Hey, I'm talking to you.

802
00:41:27,847 --> 00:41:28,486
Xiang Zhong,

803
00:41:28,487 --> 00:41:30,366
you can ask Haiyang about it

804
00:41:30,367 --> 00:41:31,806
when he has recovered,

805
00:41:31,807 --> 00:41:32,645
okay?

806
00:41:32,646 --> 00:41:34,205
I won't ask him.
I'll only ask you about it.

807
00:41:34,206 --> 00:41:35,205
What's the issue here?

808
00:41:35,206 --> 00:41:36,376
Explain yourself.

809
00:41:38,566 --> 00:41:39,896
Tell me.

810
00:41:41,166 --> 00:41:42,257
Xiang Zhong,

811
00:41:43,246 --> 00:41:45,806
when Haiyang knew
that you wanted to cancel the rent,

812
00:41:45,807 --> 00:41:47,165
he told me to find

813
00:41:47,166 --> 00:41:48,936
my classmate,
who was a real estate agent.

814
00:41:49,206 --> 00:41:50,657
When we analyzed the case,

815
00:41:50,686 --> 00:41:52,776
we thought

816
00:41:52,807 --> 00:41:54,936
that the house you rented
was too cheap to be true.

817
00:41:55,086 --> 00:41:56,737
That's why we tried to inquire about it.

818
00:41:56,807 --> 00:41:58,217
Xiang Zhong, do you know this?

819
00:41:58,367 --> 00:42:01,697
Actually, the house was haunted.

820
00:42:02,646 --> 00:42:03,286
Two years ago,

821
00:42:03,287 --> 00:42:04,565
the female tenant

822
00:42:04,566 --> 00:42:05,406
was murdered by her boyfriend

823
00:42:05,407 --> 00:42:06,617
in it.

824
00:42:06,767 --> 00:42:08,406
But Haiyang told me
not to tell you about it.

825
00:42:08,407 --> 00:42:09,806
It's because he knew

826
00:42:09,807 --> 00:42:11,137
that Uncle rented the house for you.

827
00:42:11,246 --> 00:42:12,286
He was afraid that you two
might have a conflict

828
00:42:12,287 --> 00:42:13,416
because of this.

829
00:42:18,967 --> 00:42:19,896
Thank...

830
00:42:20,807 --> 00:42:21,486
Thank you.

831
00:42:21,487 --> 00:42:22,776
You guys have done me a huge favor.

832
00:42:23,086 --> 00:42:24,217
So,

833
00:42:25,206 --> 00:42:27,816
head inside and look after him
on my behalf.

834
00:42:27,887 --> 00:42:29,296
Call me if you need anything.

835
00:42:30,246 --> 00:42:31,296
Xiang Zhong,

836
00:42:33,887 --> 00:42:36,976
actually, Haiyang still sees you

837
00:42:38,287 --> 00:42:39,165
as

838
00:42:39,166 --> 00:42:40,617
the most important person in his life.

839
00:43:23,014 --> 00:43:25,690
♪Something will eventually be lost♪

840
00:43:26,549 --> 00:43:29,072
♪Never to be remembered♪

841
00:43:30,243 --> 00:43:33,290
♪The intermittent news drifting away♪

842
00:43:33,727 --> 00:43:36,440
♪And then forgotten♪

843
00:43:37,174 --> 00:43:40,498
♪Who can still face life?♪

844
00:43:40,905 --> 00:43:43,458
♪With the courage it gives♪

845
